        siteProperty - your site property string
        startDate - date string with format "yyyy-MM-dd"

        country - country code string
        rowLimit - limit the number of rows returned by the API. The API maximum limit is 5000.
        requestedDimensions - requested dimensions of the API call.
        filters - a list of filters. Include the country filter if you need it, even though you've provided the country string.
